dct_description_sm: Relief on North Island shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Depths shown by contours and bathymetric tints. Panel title. Includes legend, place name index and street indexes, color illustrations, and location map. "Very special thanks so Sean Bardsley & Lizzy Baker of Raumati Beach; Emma & Cads of Auckland; and Arnold & Jocelyne of Te Ana."
dct_publisher_sm: Richmond, B.C. : ITMB Pub., International Travel Maps, 2008.
